edde90","tid":289161,"uid":88023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你係咪諗多左 因為你對佢好 佢會中意你<br />\n你都識講佢被動 咁始終都有一方做下主動既<br />\n又唔了解你 好感完 咪完囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔介意做主動<br />\n不過每次約佢，佢都要諗好耐，我承認我心急會問佢到底去唔去。不過我係覺得，其實食個飯姐，到底有咩野要諗咁耐<br />\n<br />\n到最後唔係我諗多左 佢話對我有過好感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗清楚者,<br />\n無意思既唔想俾假希望人<br />\n兼夾傲嬌格想人氹多兩句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a6013df7e3a9f4fa0a619c0880d36cbdbee393","tid":289161,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:40:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5f0f6ee43b9ea4ef92599dce1b9c4612db78345","tid":289161,"uid":88023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OBAThI6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOBAThI6.jpg&h=c9dad9d6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我應我係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f506884023181cb3ad3764cf718b9a240ce584e","tid":289161,"uid":88023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T17:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"